manage to get

36:55.317 --> 36:57.684
a print off that woman's cell phone?

36:57.719 --> 37:00.421
They did.
But it was only a partial,

37:00.455 --> 37:03.123
which is as good as nothing
without a suspect in custody.

37:03.158 --> 37:04.241
Anything else?

37:04.259 --> 37:06.160
No. Good night,
madam President.

37:06.194 --> 37:08.045
Good night.

37:10.314 --> 37:11.381
Olivia.

37:11.399 --> 37:12.783
So you finally got

37:12.817 --> 37:14.384
a President that'll do
your bidding.

37:14.418 --> 37:15.685
Didn't your mama ever
teach you to share?

37:15.720 --> 37:17.587
We're supposed to be in this together.
We had a deal.

37:17.621 --> 37:20.423
Am I the pot or this kettle
in this here dealio?

37:21.776 --> 37:23.526
You took down Verna.

37:24.244 --> 37:26.045
You drew first blood.
You and Verna turned on me

37:26.079 --> 37:29.048
when you conspired to save
Lindsay Dwyer behind my back.

37:29.099 --> 37:30.516
I believe everything
that comes after now,

37:30.551 --> 37:33.186
well, that's just what they
call... (Whispers) fair game.

37:35.638 --> 37:37.839
Your boy really went crazy tonight.

37:37.874 --> 37:39.958
He stopped by two baby stores.
At the first place,

37:39.992 --> 37:41.460
he made the clerk explain
how to put in a car seat.

37:41.494 --> 37:42.844
It was... thrilling.

37:42.879 --> 37:43.746
Where is he now?

37:43.780 --> 37:45.680
Probably still at the baby store.
You want me to go back?

37:47.683 --> 37:50.285
That's okay.
You can stop watching him.

37:52.688 --> 37:54.106
At least for now.

37:55.708 --> 37:57.676
The slow nipples work
for most newborns.

37:58.127 --> 37:59.744
- Is it a boy or a girl?
- A girl.

37:59.779 --> 38:01.229
- Congratulations.
-Thanks.

38:01.247 --> 38:02.964
If you have any questions,
I'll be right around the corner.

38:02.982 --> 38:04.666
Thank you.

38:05.200 --> 38:06.751
Okay. Where were we?

38:06.785 --> 38:09.103
Something about the national
election being rigged,

38:09.138 --> 38:11.022
which you say you can prove.

38:11.056 --> 38:13.124
Yes, what I can't prove is who
on the Grant team knew about it.

38:13.175 --> 38:14.375
Does your husband know
you're looking into this?

38:14.409 --> 38:15.693
He offered me a baby.

38:15.727 --> 38:16.761
He hates babies.

38:17.095 --> 38:19.279
- So he knows.
- He'll be watching you.

38:19.497 --> 38:21.498
Which is why
I need you to take this.

38:21.533 --> 38:22.949
And this is?

38:22.967 --> 38:25.819
The memory card I stole from
the voting machine in defiance.

38:25.854 --> 38:26.954
Lose it and we bungle

38:26.988 --> 38:28.488
the biggest story
since Watergate.

38:28.506 --> 38:29.890
Keep it...

38:29.924 --> 38:32.743
And we bring down an entire
administration together.

38:32.777 --> 38:33.961
I need to go.

38:33.995 --> 38:35.095
Yeah.

