40:57.650 --> 40:59.752
Not even the name of the
man in the red hoodie?

41:05.942 --> 41:08.694
I could give you my
letter of resignation

41:09.729 --> 41:11.079
or I could give you the name

41:11.113 --> 41:13.114
of the man who tried
to kill the President.

41:13.149 --> 41:14.749
The most wanted man
in the world,

41:14.784 --> 41:16.384
your Osama Bin Laden.

41:16.418 --> 41:18.019
One pill makes you larger.

41:18.037 --> 41:19.721
One pill makes you small.

41:26.311 --> 41:28.162
