listen to me right now.

41:37.623 --> 41:40.324
She will not get away with this.
We will find her.

41:40.359 --> 41:43.594
We will find her.

41:45.497 --> 41:48.265
I don't know why we're not
telling the FBI about Becky.

41:48.800 --> 41:50.134
Won't do any good.
She's in the wind.

41:50.185 --> 41:51.568
So? They could mobilize

41:51.603 --> 41:52.736
